sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User
    participant SquidPA as Squid Product Architect
    participant SquidSWE as Squid SWE + Tester
    participant Workflow as Workflow Orchestrator
    participant Cache as CacheAgent
    participant Validator as QueryValidator
    participant Executor as QueryExecution
    participant Rule as Rule + Learner
    participant HumanGate as HumanInterventionGate
    participant Human as Human Reviewer
    participant FHIR as FHIR Server

    Note over User,SquidPA: Planning Phase (one-time or on spec change)
    User->>SquidPA: /squid-plan specs/fhir-query-validator-factory.md
    SquidPA->>SquidPA: Analyzes all agent specs + architecture
    SquidPA->>User: Produces detailed Task Plan + ADR
    User->>SquidPA: Approve plan (Human Gate 1)

    Note over SquidSWE,Workflow: Implementation Phase (Squid pipeline)
    SquidSWE->>Workflow: Implement / update orchestrator + agent wiring
    SquidSWE->>Cache: Implement CacheAgent (ETag/304, TTL)
    SquidSWE->>Validator: Implement validation + pattern hooks
    SquidSWE->>Executor: Implement safe query execution
    SquidSWE->>Rule: Implement Rule + Search Learner logic
    SquidSWE->>HumanGate: Implement pause/resume + context packaging

    Note over Workflow,Human: Runtime Flow (example with escalation)
    User->>Workflow: Submit query (query_url + server_key + mode)
    Workflow->>Cache: Get CapabilityStatement (cache or fetch)
    Cache->>FHIR: GET /metadata (with If-None-Match if ETag exists)
    FHIR-->>Cache: 200 or 304
    Cache-->>Workflow: CapabilityStatement + cache_status

    Workflow->>Validator: Validate query against CapabilityStatement
    alt Query invalid or pattern detected
        Validator->>Rule: Report failure + context
        Rule->>Rule: Check thresholds (3/10min to learner, 5/15min to human)
        alt Learner triggered
            Rule->>Rule: Generate suggestions
            Rule-->>Workflow: Learner output
        else Human escalation required
            Rule->>HumanGate: Trigger with full context
            HumanGate->>Human: Present query, errors, history, learner suggestions
            Human->>HumanGate: Decision (approve / reject / modify)
            HumanGate-->>Workflow: Resume with decision
        end
    else Query valid
        alt mode == validate_and_execute
            Workflow->>Executor: Execute query
            Executor->>FHIR: GET validated query_url
            FHIR-->>Executor: Bundle or error
            Executor-->>Workflow: Structured results + metadata
        end
    end

    Workflow-->>User: Final structured output + full audit trail
